room_title: Escape room "Operation K.E.Y.C.A.R.D" by The Art of Escape: ICT in Wichita
room_description: One of the agents was spotted communicating with Foreign Officials. What is his agenda? The last tracking mission puts his at Hotel Thames in London. You will have to go undercover, infiltrate the room, find any clues to his plans and get out undetected.
